{"tid":1055911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚇親媽媽】男童瞞父母攬寵物金魚瞓 愛牠變成殺死牠！","createTime":"2019-03-10T23:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T03:56:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b15e050dca8393e2b60c221404084de8b97efad","tid":1055911,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T23:11:18.000Z","msg":"美國喬治亞州4歲男孩哈姆林（Everett Hamlin）因為想擁着自己的金魚一起睡，竟把牠從魚缸內拿出來，意外殺死了自己心愛的金魚。父母事後向他解釋，他知道真相後非常傷心。<br />\n枉死的金魚「Nemo」早在哈姆林只有數個月大時已開始飼養，哈姆林一直很喜歡牠。沒料有天他踏上椅子，伸手入魚缸捉牠，並抱着牠到自己的床一起睡覺。當媽媽托麗（Tori）看見魚缸旁有一張椅子時，感到很奇怪，很快發覺「Nemo」不見了。她和丈夫一起搜索，最後發現牠死在兒子的手中。<br />\n兩人急忙叫醒兒子，向他解釋「Nemo」的死因，哈姆林連番說自己只想擁抱呵護牠，當明白金魚被拿出來會因缺水而死的時侯，感到很傷心。<br />\n托麗說：「起初我感到驚訝，但當他稱只是想擁抱金魚時，我就覺得，我的天呀，這真的很慘，他殺了牠一點都不有趣。他不知自己在做甚麼，但坦白說，他捉到金魚我很意外，他有點技巧，可能金魚習慣見到他在魚缸旁邊而感到放鬆。」<br />\n事後托麗把故事分享到網上，並讓哈姆林重新買一條金魚，哈姆林亦保證不會碰新買的金魚了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190309/large/1552128687_e5dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190309%2Flarge%2F1552128687_e5dc.jpg&h=edfd9c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190309/large/1552128687_b72e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190309%2Flarge%2F1552128687_b72e.jpg&h=07146886&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8720a7e5cfdf69023ffd1f348472db8778da09c","tid":1055911,"uid":188155,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T23:14:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f13cd9c1d70f93ac0310eba78b2b5bc4a018ff3f","tid":1055911,"uid":55386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T23:58:37.000Z","msg":"魚魚rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b3c39e154d07ad7e39cf732face51054053ceb","tid":1055911,"uid":25556,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"好慘但又好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c67d3a73f2130fc77eefdd774a9e727e4e2c93b","tid":1055911,"uid":54597,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"條魚有啲似紅衫魚"},{"pid":"cf548f381b253cd10ceb0444ab1e8503c69b4e35","tid":1055911,"uid":125479,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"天真得只有你 令神仙魚歸天要怪誰<br />\n以為留在原地不夠遨遊 就讓牠沙灘裡戲水"},{"pid":"3c12575183b619b514c13639f4cb5932c44ef360","tid":1055911,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"放入個口搵口水浸佢"},{"pid":"6033ec1876c9c3bccaa78f28a72b4ab1881aeedd","tid":1055911,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07b3c39e154d07ad7e39cf732face51054053ceb","tid":1055911,"uid":25556,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"好慘但又好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dce8eb205a896c774ba89d9a2a626532ae15909","tid":1055911,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"大個應該唔會食魚"},{"pid":"dded6407a918cd812419177071be3bf9f1f44372","tid":1055911,"uid":31094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa0c8b95f482bc8515bf2dff983643bf0db30b6","tid":1055911,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"Finding nemo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e431a76ce5f784c025384eb2e89164484928c613","tid":1055911,"uid":7262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"大個會捉左女神做寵物攬實佢"},{"pid":"6da1